body_html:
The latest anaconda package (tensorflow 1.8) does not show the slowdown anymore, with timings back in line to what 1.4.1 was; so this issue can be closed.

However, it would be great if (an adequate variation of) the test above could be added as a regression test to ensure that the problem doesn't come back.
